href="https://www.istockphoto.com/illustrations/connection" itemtype="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Connection icons</a></li><li class="YL6NAWO3Y2FUpbullA12"><a class="pAyfNrZR1Tr3C52VGKph" data-testid="categoryPill" href="https://www.istockphoto.com/illustrations/connection" itemtype="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Connection silhouettes</a></li><li class="YL6NAWO3Y2FUpbullA12"><a class="pAyfNrZR1Tr3C52VGKph" data-testid="categoryPill" href="https://www.istockphoto.com/illustrations/connection" itemtype="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Connection clipart</a></li><li class="YL6NAWO3Y2FUpbullA12"><a class="pAyfNrZR1Tr3C52VGKph" data-testid="categoryPill" href="https://www.istockphoto.com/illustrations/connection" itemtype="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Connection symbols</a></li><li class="YL6NAWO3Y2FUpbullA12"><a class="pAyfNrZR1Tr3C52VGKph" data-testid="categoryPill" href="https://www.istockphoto.com/illustrations/connection" itemtype="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Connection borders</a></li><li class="YL6NAWO3Y2FUpbullA12"><a class="pAyfNrZR1Tr3C52VGKph" data-testid="categoryPill" href="https://www.istockphoto.com/illustrations/connection" itemtype="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Connection patterns</a></li></ul></div></section><section class="SopHNW0D5OHB6nbAraBB eavxFCLmyEbUpegAMab0 sW8bB2gMhW68rhXx5lzT AW9vrB_8tP_5cOETgR_Q geGNh3ziQ2SI2d7cx6Zs"><div class="SopHNW0D5OHB6nbAraBB k57WuB2z7_OJFIiDNWR_ sW8bB2gMhW68rhXx5lzT BDc0iW8Maze62lL67F3F"><div data-testid="faq-section" class="SopHNW0D5OHB6nbAraBB dMK4CGeVyOoIr4oiIpBB geGNh3ziQ2SI2d7cx6Zs"><div><h2 class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL WUM7gxcqSbLENMf1N_G4 wSGyCMp9LJPyNSkg_7Jh">Frequently asked questions</h2><hr class="Gjt5DuitXXi3EZpex1Ck"><dl><dt class="NiAAuv8sF_qL4fnFFine"><span class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL AAbCqDZ1jv_hxiIWF4cA">What's a royalty-free license?</span></dt><dd class="b4BCOSlrOYMD8qHNkiBo"><div class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL N_tzVDQ4vCrOALW7QCdR xAYpRrtihdkDPZ7Fo7AS"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">Royalty-free licenses let you pay once to use copyrighted images and video clips in personal and commercial projects on an ongoing basis without requiring additional payments each time you use that content. It's a win-win, and it's why everything on iStock is only available royalty-free — including all <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/photos/connection">Connection</a> images and footage.</span></div></dd><dt class="NiAAuv8sF_qL4fnFFine"><span class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL AAbCqDZ1jv_hxiIWF4cA">What kinds of royalty-free files are available on iStock?</span></dt><dd class="b4BCOSlrOYMD8qHNkiBo"><div class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL N_tzVDQ4vCrOALW7QCdR xAYpRrtihdkDPZ7Fo7AS"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">Royalty-free licenses are the best option for anyone who needs to use stock images commercially, which is why every file on iStock — whether it’s a <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/stock-photos">photo</a>, <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/stock-illustrations">illustration</a> or <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/footage">video clip</a> — is only available royalty-free.</span></div></dd><dt class="NiAAuv8sF_qL4fnFFine"><span class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL AAbCqDZ1jv_hxiIWF4cA">How can you use royalty-free images and video clips?</span></dt><dd class="b4BCOSlrOYMD8qHNkiBo"><div class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL N_tzVDQ4vCrOALW7QCdR xAYpRrtihdkDPZ7Fo7AS"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">From social media ads to billboards, PowerPoint presentations to feature films, you're free to modify, resize and customize every asset on iStock — including all <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/photos/connection">Connection</a> images and footage — to fit your projects. With the exception of "Editorial use only" photos (which can only be used in editorial projects and can't be modified), the possibilities are limitless.</span></div></dd></dl><hr class="l6RmUz0LTXhB98ZmWUXx"></div></div><p data-testid="learn-more-section" class="q6fz6v6TujBl09iQL8xL hhsb43ABEiOJMIDVAc7Q FmmXxEeaLXJQtyiKuNgs"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">Learn more about <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/royalty-free-images">royalty-free images</a> or view <a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/faq/using-files#photos">FAQs related to stock photos</a>.</span></p></div></section></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--/$--></div>
